# 🍰 Pastry Website

This project is a visually engaging pastry shop website developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, with a strong emphasis on advanced animations powered by the GSAP (GreenSock Animation Platform) library.

It was designed to enhance user experience through smooth transitions, interactive elements, and modern UI design, while exploring the capabilities of animation in front-end development.

---

## ✨ Features
- Responsive and modern user interface  
- Product showcase for pastries and bakery items  
- Smooth and dynamic animations using GSAP  
- Interactive and engaging user experience  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript  
- GSAP (GreenSock Animation Platform)  

---

## 🎯 Project Objective
The primary objective of this project is to apply and deepen my understanding of front-end development by integrating advanced animation techniques. It focuses on creating visually appealing interfaces while maintaining clean, structured, and maintainable code.

---

## 📌 Conclusion
This project reflects my ability to combine design and functionality to build engaging web interfaces, as well as my commitment to continuously improving my front-end development skills.
